abstract: UBS reports fourth-quarter profit of 949 million Swiss francs, or around $929 million, up 11 percent from 858 million francs in year-earlier period; warns of challenging macroeconomic and geopolitical outlook.

headline.print_headline: UBS Posts 11% Profit Gain, but It Issues a Warning on Market’s Headwinds
headline.main: UBS Posts 11% Profit Gain, but Issues Warning on Market’s Headwinds

snippet: The Swiss bank said uncertainty in the markets cut into the results of its wealth management and investment banking businesses.
lead_paragraph: The Swiss bank said uncertainty in the markets cut into the results of its wealth management and investment banking businesses.
